cs.NI, cs.DS, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper deals with wireless sensor networks and their coverage problem. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper proposes heuristic algorithms to solve the target coverage problem. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a new greedy heuristic algorithm. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with maximizing the lifetime of the network while monitoring targets, which can be seen as a control problem. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a less likely category but still possible as the paper proposes a new algorithm that prioritizes sensors based on residual battery life, which can be seen as a learning-based approach.
